.TH "nvmf_context_set_fabrics_config" 9 "nvmf_context_set_fabrics_config" "March 2026" "libnvme API manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
nvmf_context_set_fabrics_config \- Set fabrics configuration for context
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "int" nvmf_context_set_fabrics_config
.BI "(struct nvmf_context *fctx "  ","
.BI "struct nvme_fabrics_config *cfg "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "fctx" 12
Fabrics context
.IP "cfg" 12
Fabrics configuration to apply
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
Applies the given fabrics configuration to the context.
.SH "RETURN"
0 on success, or a negative error code on failure.
